                            <h2 class="title">
                                How Do We Use Your Information?
                            </h2>
                            <p class="desc">
                                We use your information to deliver services to current and potential clients, manage
                                administrative tasks and client relationships (including knowledge management and
                                service promotion), and comply with legal requirements. We may involve trusted
                                third-party service providers for specific tasks like data processing or office
                                services. These providers are bound by strict contracts to ensure the security of your
                                information and its use solely for RemoteHiringHunt's service delivery.

                            </p>
                            <p class="desc mt-3 ">
                                We treat your information confidentially and do not share it with any third party
                                without your consent, except as required by law. We also have procedures in place to
                                securely delete or get rid of information when it's no longer needed
                            </p>
